dialogs.text:
Welcome to Zelia!
Press space or   
left click mouse 
to remove dialogs

Use arrow keys or
  a/s/d keys to  
   run and jump

Use mouse pointer to aim
 and left click to fire

Heal hearts restore health.
  Max hearts add max HP.   
Mana potions add max mana.

Fire magic can break 
   some surfaces

...and some surfaces   
 break just by touching
      them...

Press and hold up-arrow or w-key 
   while jumping or airborne    
       to start flying.         
Use mouse-pointer for direction.

Press middle mouse button     
to create a magic barrier     
Use mouse cursor for direction

Hold right mouse button to 
     heal yourself

Hold left and right button  
For extra strong Light Magic.
Explode Earth Magic platform
with Light Magic.
